body: "pure fn" is perhaps not the best name, because it can have side effects. Just calling it *function* might be enough (as opposed to a *method* on a module).
body_html: "pure fn" is perhaps not the best name, because it can have side effects. Just calling it function might be enough (as opposed to a method on a module).
